snippet.title: Trailer | Smash 1
snippet.description:
Super Smash Bros. 1, or Smash 1 for short, is an ode to Smash 64, in the form of a Brawl Mod. 

Links

Wii Build: http://forums.kc-mm.com/Gallery/BrawlView.php?Number=220676

Netplay Build: http://forums.kc-mm.com/Gallery/BrawlView.php?Number=220675

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Smash1Official

Discord: https://discord.gg/hb8sWqpFVA

Special thanks to Gael Romo for artwork in this video

And Nugget VA and J-BoZ for narration.
